litical movements among the new independent countries of the vast East European-Eurasian region.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aHistory -- European. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Great Britain / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080477926540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804779265423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804779265/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles